          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1626951088014-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the<strong> smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium, add the<strong> drained black beans</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span><strong> warm water</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 10-12 min or until the mushrooms are cooked through</p>",
